{"tid":1786884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★HK No IT】19年12月17日---警冚旺角鹹碟舖檢20萬元貨","createTime":"2019-12-17T13:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T06:01:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e8d303d48e6c00aad20e2f811b99b9c5d9dabf1","tid":1786884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191217/photo/bkn-20191217203712597-1217_00822_001_01p.jpg?20191217210908\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191217203712597-1217_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20191217210908&h=45ccba04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角警區特別職務隊人員根據線報及經深入調查後，於今日（17日）下午約3時，進行代號「搜鷁」的掃黃行動，突擊搜查亞皆老街一店舖，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">檢獲6500隻總值約20萬港元的色情光碟</span></strong>及約1600港元現金。行動中，警員以涉嫌「管有淫褻物品以供發布用途」及「發布淫褻物品」拘捕一名姓林(57歲)本地男子，把他帶署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191217/bkn-20191217203712597-1217_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191217%2Fbkn-20191217203712597-1217_00822_001.html&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0kuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=c0836234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191217/bkn-20191217203712597-1217_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c29d5b3e2325fa551fd1af96ea3745f2a148a169","tid":1786884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"